## API Documentation

Every endpoint must be documented in `ai-specs/specs/api-spec.yml` before implementation.

Required fields per endpoint:
- `summary` — one-line description
- `description` — full behavior including edge cases
- `requestBody` — schema with examples
- `responses` — all possible status codes with schemas
- `tags` — for grouping in documentation UI

