## Commit Messages

Format: `<type>(<scope>): <imperative description>`

Types: `feat`, `fix`, `refactor`, `test`, `docs`, `chore`, `perf`

```
feat(items): add pagination to item list endpoint
fix(auth): correct token expiry calculation for DST edge case
refactor(parser): extract tokenizer into separate module
docs(api): update OpenAPI spec for /users endpoint
```

- Maximum 72 characters for the subject line
- Body (optional): explain *why*, not *what* (the diff shows what)
- Never: "fix bug", "update", "WIP", "changes"

